title: Best Practices & Knowledge Sharing
body:
  - type: markdown
    attributes:
      value: |
        # üìö Best Practices & Knowledge Sharing

        Share proven patterns, techniques, and workflows for using {{ image.name }} effectively.
        
        This discussion category is for educational content and expert knowledge from the community.

  - type: textarea
    id: topic-title
    attributes:
      label: Topic/Best Practice Title
      description: What best practice or technique are you sharing?
      placeholder: "Securing Multi-Layer Docker Images with {{ image.name }}"
      validations:
        required: true

  - type: textarea
    id: overview
    attributes:
      label: Overview
      description: Provide a concise overview of the best practice
      placeholder: |
        This guide covers how to implement security best practices when scaffolding Docker images, including layer optimization, dependency scanning, and vulnerability management.
      validations:
        required: true

  - type: textarea
    id: step-by-step
    attributes:
      label: Step-by-Step Guide
      description: Provide detailed steps or instructions
      placeholder: |
        ## Step 1: Setup
        [Instructions]

        ## Step 2: Implementation
        [Instructions]

        ## Step 3: Verification
        [Instructions]

        ## Best Practices
        - [ ] Do this
        - [ ] Avoid that
      validations:
        required: true

  - type: textarea
    id: code-examples
    attributes:
      label: Code Examples
      description: Provide configuration or code examples
      render: yaml
      placeholder: |
        # Example Dockerfile
        FROM ubuntu:latest
        # Best practice: ...
        RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
          package1 \
          package2

  - type: textarea
    id: common-pitfalls
    attributes:
      label: Common Pitfalls & How to Avoid Them
      description: What mistakes should people watch out for?
      placeholder: |
        ### ‚ùå Mistake 1: [Description]
        This causes: [Problem]
        ‚úÖ Solution: [How to avoid]

        ### ‚ùå Mistake 2: [Description]
        This causes: [Problem]
        ‚úÖ Solution: [How to avoid]

  - type: textarea
    id: performance-tips
    attributes:
      label: Performance Tips & Optimization
      description: Any performance considerations or optimizations?
      placeholder: |
        - Caching strategy: ...
        - Layer ordering: ...
        - Size optimization: ...

  - type: textarea
    id: tools-resources
    attributes:
      label: Recommended Tools & Resources
      description: Tools, scripts, or documentation that support this practice
      placeholder: |
        - Tool: [Name] - [Link] - [Why it's useful]
        - Documentation: [Link]
        - Related discussion: #[number]

  - type: textarea
    id: questions
    attributes:
      label: Questions & Discussion Points
      description: What questions should the community consider?
      placeholder: |
        - How does this apply to your use case?
        - What challenges have you faced?
        - Have you tested this in production?

  - type: checkboxes
    id: difficulty-level
    attributes:
      label: Difficulty Level
      description: Who is this guide best suited for?
      options:
        - label: Beginner - New to Docker
        - label: Intermediate - Basic Docker knowledge
        - label: Advanced - Expert-level techniques
      validations:
        required: true

  - type: textarea
    id: references
    attributes:
      label: References & Attribution
      description: Link to original sources, related discussions, or inspirations
      placeholder: |
        - Original source: [Link]
        - Related issue: #[number]
        - Inspired by: @[username]
